$ /dev/mdN

*md* stands for *meta disk* (but I've also seen: *multiple devices*).

? Linux supports the following *md devices*:
  • Linear
  • → Linux/filesystem/RAID 0, 1, 4, 5, 6, 10
  • Multipath
  • Faulty
  • Container

sa:

 `mdadm`

 `→ Linux/fhs/proc/mdstat`

 `→ Linux/fhs/dev`

 `/sys/block/mdX/…`

  → https://people.redhat.com/mingo/raidtools/[raidtools]
